00:54:33.470 --> 00:54:36.080
That nobody-- no
separate country,

00:54:36.080 --> 00:54:40.800
or even groups of
countries, can manage--

00:54:40.800 --> 00:54:44.720
that it's larger than the
ability of these countries

00:54:44.720 --> 00:54:45.780
to manage.

00:54:45.780 --> 00:54:50.510
So Lynn writes this before
