WILLIAM BONVILLIAN:
Yeah, I mean, Lynn

01:04:07.590 --> 01:04:10.860
is painting a dark side here.

01:04:10.860 --> 01:04:13.980
And he's painting a portrayal
of opening up the system.

01:04:13.980 --> 01:04:19.410
And then the system itself
begins to take control, right?

01:04:19.410 --> 01:04:22.440
This globalized
financial system itself

01:04:22.440 --> 01:04:25.650
begins to take
control and minimize

01:04:25.650 --> 01:04:28.170
the ability of
any of the players

01:04:28.170 --> 01:04:30.210
to impact or affect that.

01:04:30.210 --> 01:04:33.960
So it's a fundamental statement
about the fragility and lack

01:04:33.960 --> 01:04:35.460
of resilience.

01:04:35.460 --> 01:04:43.540
And your single point of failure
point is well taken, Chloe.

01:04:43.540 --> 01:04:46.350
It's a dark picture here,
and what makes it intriguing

01:04:46.350 --> 01:04:49.150
and the only reason why
