01:04:54.280 --> 01:04:57.670
And boy, that was
so close to a really

01:04:57.670 --> 01:05:02.020
massive worldwide depression
that it's painful in economy.

01:05:02.020 --> 01:05:05.560
So I put it in as kind of
a useful warning lesson,

01:05:05.560 --> 01:05:08.500
