about how we've

01:05:08.500 --> 01:05:12.100
moved in the international
organization of our economy

01:05:12.100 --> 01:05:15.070
from a nation-centered
to an ally-centered

01:05:15.070 --> 01:05:18.310
to a truly globalized
kind of orientation here.

01:05:18.310 --> 01:05:20.860
And what are the
implications of that?

01:05:20.860 --> 01:05:22.810
We need to keep
thinking about this.

01:05:22.810 --> 01:05:25.300
